---

<BaseLayout
  title="Conditions We Treat"
  description="Naturopathic support for musculoskeletal pain, chronic fatigue, digestive health, hormones, mood, respiratory health and other concerns in Bedford and Halifax, Nova Scotia."
  focusKeyword="conditions treated Halifax naturopathic"
>
  <HeroSection title="Conditions" centered compact>
    Support for acute and chronic health concerns using naturopathic assessment, lifestyle medicine, nutrition, IV therapy and regenerative injection approaches where appropriate.
  </HeroSection>

  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="section-shell">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-10 reveal">
        <p class="pill mb-4">Condition Pages</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-medium text-emerald-950 mb-4">Care Information by Condition</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
          These pages describe specific conditions seen in practice and the types of assessment or care that may be considered.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 reveal reveal-delay-100">
        {conditionPages.map((condition) => (
          <a href={condition.href} class="site-card-interactive group flex h-full flex-col gap-3 p-5 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 focus:ring-offset-2">
            <span class="inline-flex w-fit items-center rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-800">
              Condition page
            </span>
            <span class="flex items-start gap-2 text-lg font-semibold text-emerald-950 group-hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors">
              <ChevronRight class="mt-1 w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform duration-200" aria-hidden="true" />
              {condition.title}
            </span>
            <span class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">{condition.description}</span>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-emerald-50">
    <div class="section-shell">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-10 reveal">
        <p class="pill mb-4">Related Guides</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-medium text-emerald-950 mb-4">Broader Health Topics</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
          These are educational article guides, not condition landing pages. They are useful when a concern overlaps with hormones, mood, digestion, immunity or cardiometabolic health.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 reveal reveal-delay-100">
        {relatedGuides.map((guide) => (
          <a href={guide.href} class="site-card-interactive group flex h-full flex-col gap-3 p-5 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 focus:ring-offset-2">
            <span class="inline-flex w-fit items-center rounded-full bg-white px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-800 ring-1 ring-emerald-100">
              Article guide
            </span>
            <span class="flex items-start gap-2 text-lg font-semibold text-emerald-950 group-hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors">
              <ChevronRight class="mt-1 w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform duration-200" aria-hidden="true" />
              {guide.title}
            </span>
            <span class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">{guide.description}</span>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="bg-emerald-950 py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="section-shell text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-medium text-white mb-6">Don't See Your Condition Listed?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-white/90 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Dr. MacLeod works with a wide range of health concerns. Contact us to discuss whether naturopathic care is a fit for your specific situation.
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <CTAButton source="conditions-cta" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
